stnlocationdescription: Turn West onto 514 off of Hwy 41.  Go West for 6.8 km and turn south into laneway.  Park approx. 50m before bushes.  Walk SW across field; over fenceline to large; lone spruce tree ( markers 1 and 2) and follow south along clearing through forest.

Turn north off of Murray Hill Road towards the horseshoe canyon viewpoint.  Follow trail North.  Swing East across a clearing; then North again.  Park sleds at the bottom of a small hill.  Travel approx 120m on a 230 degree bearing downhill to #1.

Follow driveway into Whispering Pines Bible Camp off of Hwy 41 NE of Elkwater. Park at Church.  Follow N across field to trail off to left.  Turn left and course starts at first clearing SW of archery range.

Turn South onto Sherwood Drive off of Lakeview Drive and follow towards Elkwater Campground.  Park at Gate and walk across field past playground and washrooms.  Course starts at campsite # 18 and ends at Campsite # 28.

Travel 3.1km west of Hwy 41 on Murray Hill Road passing an information plaque at 2.9km.  Look for a gap in the trees to the North.  Park here.  Walk North across field; cross fenceline on east side of drainage.  Follow trail downhill to clearing.

Turn East on Reesor Lake Road off of Hwy 41.  Follow for 2.6 km and turn North on an old road.  Follow for 2 km and park at above lat/long.  Follow old road West down hill until intersection (# 1).  Turn North and follow old road bed along snow course.
